{"tid":2060361,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"<劇本> 零本地感染7天後恐再斷纜 祿泉樓群組1接觸者初步確診","createTime":"2020-06-11T14:46:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T13:17:56.000Z","uid":227801,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c39f01b0165e0045a4471a0346d1cc164fc21c37","tid":2060361,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T14:46:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200611&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=61039930\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200611%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D61039930&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0vSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=32368dd4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200611%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D61039930&h=37c85de6\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200611&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=61039930</a><br />\n本港疫情再趨緩和，衞生防護中心今日（11日）再度錄得零確診，亦即連續第7日沒有本地武漢肺炎個案，亦是連續第3日沒有輸入個案，累積確診仍維持1,107宗及1宗疑似個案。但據悉，本港晚上錄得1宗初步確診個案，是第1084號個案的密切接觸者，該密切接觸者早前已被送到隔離營。第1084號個案是沙田瀝源邨祿泉樓感染群組（又稱嘉里物流貨倉群組）的首名確診病人，若其密切接觸者最終確診，該群組將增至11人染疫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d453462712fb90c8147257c08d8dd4ff48f682eb","tid":2060361,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T14:48:05.000Z","msg":"延長限聚令14日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e18434dc4c07bfaf50fdc607e639141545f3634","t